Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.70,0:01:12.70,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The herbs I picked look like they've dried pretty nicely.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.70,0:01:14.01,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone want to try a taste?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.01,0:01:16.44,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You guys should try it!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.96,0:01:19.61,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Or you could make Joe drink it later!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.61,0:01:21.13,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.66,0:01:28.15,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,The black curtain for the café has \Nbeen ordered and will be delivered.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.15,0:01:32.36,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,The mural and the wall poster should be finished on time.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.36,0:01:36.41,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa. We're so behind!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.41,0:01:37.85,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.85,0:01:42.93,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,If we only work during school, I don't think we'll finish on time.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.93,0:01:44.09,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,I think we will.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.87,0:01:47.79,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sadako still hasn't come back.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.79,0:01:49.84,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.84,0:01:51.55,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,I just saw her earlier.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.55,0:01:56.50,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! She looked like she wasn't feeling \Ntoo well, but she said not to worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.50,0:01:57.88,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.36,0:02:01.49,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's that herb you have there?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.49,0:02:03.41,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,This is the chameleon plant{http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Houttuynia_cordata} and Thunberg's geranium {http://jisho.org/words?jap=%E7%8F%BE%E3%81%AE%E8%A8%BC%E6%8B%A0&eng=&dict=edict}.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.41,0:02:05.42,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,They're good for treating diuresis and constipation, I think.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.42,0:02:06.83,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu, do you want to try some?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.83,0:02:08.15,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.21,0:02:19.30,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Here Andy, take this one too.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.30,0:02:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. {zwill this was me.}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.69,0:02:23.24,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.24,0:02:24.76,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Ryu!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.76,0:02:27.18,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I haven't been able to help out.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.18,0:02:29.08,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright. You couldn't have skipped practice!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.08,0:02:31.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you guys have summer preliminaries \Nright after the school festival, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.52,0:02:35.55,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what were doing about the bottom part over here?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.55,0:02:36.89,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Which part?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.89,0:02:37.50,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.50,0:02:38.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Were we going to run wire through it for reinforcement? {school projects can't live without chicken wire}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.14,0:02:42.62,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know… You'd have to ask Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.62,0:02:45.31,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Where is that guy?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.31,0:02:48.06,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like him to skip.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.70,0:02:58.84,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Shota!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.30,0:03:02.70,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.93,0:03:06.12,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Everyone's already started working, haven't they?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.12,0:03:07.07,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.07,0:03:10.18,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I think there was something they needed to ask you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.18,0:03:11.29,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.22,0:03:18.15,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Did you go confront her?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.32,0:03:24.14,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.49,0:03:26.76,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I got rejected. {the fuck, Ryuu's foot is bigger than his head. come on IG}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.61,0:03:32.64,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I was annoying to her after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.98,0:03:38.11,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't want people to get the wrong idea about us.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.65,0:03:46.19,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I think she felt that all of the things I did \Nfor her were making other people suspicious.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.22,0:03:54.04,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to tell her how I feel and how much \NI care for her, but it didn't work out.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.00,0:03:58.48,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't hold it in anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.75,0:04:03.59,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.59,0:04:07.51,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts more than I thought it would.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.08,0:04:14.17,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I was annoying enough to make her cry like that. {lit: i didn't think i was that much of an annoyance to her that i'd make her cry like that}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.52,0:04:25.43,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot! {lit: bitch}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.14,0:04:39.88,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,You look terrible.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.36,0:04:48.20,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.56,0:04:53.60,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Friends? More like rivals!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.30,0:04:59.65,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya rejected me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.86,0:05:03.26,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.18,0:05:08.42,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think we're friends now or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.42,0:05:09.99,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't group yourself with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.13,0:05:13.70,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're not my rival.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.33,0:05:20.71,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Let go of me!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.15,0:05:30.35,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Because I was rejected?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.55,0:05:35.69,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,More like because you didn't try.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.41,0:05:40.03,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Because you hurt him!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.53,0:05:42.97,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Hurt him?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.02,0:05:45.49,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I hurt him?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.32,0:05:50.49,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Because I couldn't leave him alone even though he likes someone? {lit: even though he likes someone, he had to continue paying attention to me}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.78,0:05:52.74,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Because I bothered hi—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.96,0:05:56.66,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're an idiot! {lit: dense}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.89,0:06:04.13,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't Kazehaya the only one who never looked at you out of pity?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.21,0:06:10.00,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Even though even Chizu and Ayane did!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.84,0:06:15.10,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Open your eyes! {lit: what are you looking at that you have such opinions about him}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.36,0:06:17.99,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,What…?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.39,0:06:22.44,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,You are not the same as me.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.08,0:06:25.73,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I told him.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.66,0:06:27.92,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.45,0:06:35.75,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he rejected me, I clearly told him how I felt!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.87,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare put yourself on the same level as me!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.99,0:06:56.31,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've always, always been watching Kazehaya,{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.64,0:07:02.46,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}sometimes even without noticing it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.31,0:07:06.02,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,That was delicious.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.02,0:07:08.72,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako's curry is the best!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.72,0:07:10.11,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It was hayashi rice, wasn't it? {http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hayashi_rice}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.11,0:07:11.18,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Haeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:29.01,Phone,,0000,0000,0000,,From: Chizuru Yoshida       Title: Now!\NSorry for the short notice, but we're meeting at my house to make the costumes for the costume parade. If you're free, come over!\N
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.07,0:07:44.06,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,W-Would it be alright if I went over to Chizu's house right now?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.06,0:07:46.06,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Now?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.06,0:07:47.76,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Are you preparing for the school festival?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.76,0:07:48.56,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.56,0:07:50.35,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,For the costume parade.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.35,0:07:51.58,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Costume?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.58,0:07:55.64,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I have some snacks for you to take over then.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.64,0:07:56.49,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Snacks?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.01,0:07:58.92,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful walking at night!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.92,0:08:01.27,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, be careful.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.27,0:08:02.50,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I will!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.98,0:08:05.87,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.76,0:08:10.98,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Her school festival…
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.98,0:08:15.01,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I remember helping to make our class \Nfloat back when I was in high school. {dashi can be soup stock or parade float - dad thinks it's the latter but mom means the former. how can we pun this ;_;}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.01,0:08:18.77,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I did the refreshment booth.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.77,0:08:22.51,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Dried bonito and seaweed{http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kombu - want to use seaweed?}, big Shiitake mushrooms and dried sea slugs.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.51,0:08:23.98,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What? Oh, soup stock?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.98,0:08:28.24,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It was so hard to cut the Shiitake!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.24,0:08:31.99,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,That's a delicious sounding…float? Soup?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.57,0:08:33.95,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let anyone see us!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.95,0:08:35.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Quietly now, quietly!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.82,0:08:39.58,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's stuck!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Lift it up!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.44,0:08:43.62,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.62,0:08:48.46,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure taking your floats out is against the rules.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.46,0:08:51.15,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Pin! Pretend you didn't see us!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.15,0:08:53.45,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Every other class is doing it!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.45,0:08:55.36,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We won't finish on time otherwise!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.36,0:08:56.67,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're our homeroom teacher!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.67,0:08:59.22,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I don't really care.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.73,0:09:01.23,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What does he mean by that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.23,0:09:02.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He's supposed to be our teacher.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.21,0:09:08.19,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Just warning you, you guys better not get caught \Nby another teacher. I don't want to deal with it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.69,0:09:11.08,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Phew, safe for now. But what do we do about this?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.08,0:09:12.41,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Lift that side first.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.41,0:09:13.56,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.95,0:09:16.11,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Shota!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.11,0:09:19.62,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,You're more of a jerk than I thought.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.62,0:09:22.10,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,When did you get like that? {you become like that}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.10,0:09:22.92,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.92,0:09:24.26,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "what" me!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.26,0:09:28.29,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,You pretend to care, then make the other \Nperson care for real... You're scary.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.29,0:09:30.97,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,And yet you look so harmless…
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.97,0:09:33.38,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,You rejected Kuronuma, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.38,0:09:34.80,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I was rejected!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.80,0:09:37.13,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,You totally fooled me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.13,0:09:40.71,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you went off so fast to reject someone.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.71,0:09:44.08,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what do you plan on doing in the future?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.08,0:09:45.18,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Becoming a gigolo?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.18,0:09:46.32,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,A host?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.32,0:09:47.33,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe a—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.33,0:09:49.31,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one that got rejected!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.89,0:09:52.40,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.92,0:09:54.11,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I. Was. Rejected!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.61,0:09:59.16,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,What? Did you run over there just to turn her down?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.71,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.71,0:10:03.10,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.10,0:10:05.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did Pin catch you?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.74,0:10:08.05,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! You guys go on ahead!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.05,0:10:08.83,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.84,0:10:19.05,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I went to confess to her.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.18,0:10:23.00,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,It just… didn't go well.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.38,0:10:28.31,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I was rejected.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.04,0:10:33.23,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.23,0:10:38.04,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,So you weren't able to really say it. You just tiptoed around it.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.36,0:10:41.41,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,What a pansy.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.41,0:10:44.48,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I said everything I had to!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.13,0:10:46.75,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. It's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.75,0:10:47.87,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.61,0:10:51.04,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.04,0:10:55.40,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,You said before that you don't understand Kuronuma,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.40,0:10:58.55,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,but really, you already have trouble with yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.29,0:11:01.38,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine like this, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.81,0:11:03.49,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up on her.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.10,0:11:21.70,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's weird.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.99,0:11:23.87,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't match.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.87,0:11:26.19,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.31,0:11:33.83,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,That's because it should probably be like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.92,0:11:38.84,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh no! I jumped into their conversation!{\i0} {girl you must have grease on your feet, 'cause you went sliding into their conversation.}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.95,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.95,0:11:42.23,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It fits now!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.86,0:11:44.30,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Sadako!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.76,0:11:54.85,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go bring us some drinks.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.05,0:12:04.49,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.37,0:12:08.12,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.96,0:12:10.05,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Um…
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.87,0:12:14.29,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.92,0:12:19.46,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for texting me and inviting me over…
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.16,0:12:22.97,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,and for what you said after school.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.75,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,You have us!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.75,0:12:29.43,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How long do you plan on putting yourself down for?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.40,0:12:33.14,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,It made me really happy to hear you say that.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.28,0:12:50.38,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Last year, when I first became friends with you and Ayane,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.38,0:12:58.29,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,that was the first time I ever felt that someone liked me! {s-so pretty ;_;}{what about your parents!}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.56,0:13:02.84,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I said it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.79,0:13:15.52,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.14,0:13:19.00,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Now, for those drinks!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.47,0:13:23.17,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that great?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.17,0:13:26.03,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Look how happy she is after hearing you say that.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.86,0:13:30.70,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing me say that?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.39,0:13:32.79,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing me…say it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.52,0:13:36.25,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I told him.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.25,0:13:38.99,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I clearly told him!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.92,0:13:49.63,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did I…tell him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.64,0:13:55.78,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did Kazehaya hear me say it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.65,0:14:13.76,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kurumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.76,0:14:14.70,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morn—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.54,0:14:19.21,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}S-She turned away from me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.11,0:14:23.15,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.12,0:14:25.13,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.56,0:14:27.88,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! I-I…!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.88,0:14:31.14,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I showed you such an embarrassing side of me yesterday!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.14,0:14:32.42,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.42,0:14:33.43,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Actually—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.43,0:14:34.60,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there. {stop right there criminal scum}{HOLD IT, TEAM ROCKET! GIVE BACK MY PIKACHU!}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.60,0:14:37.32,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You've really done it now.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.35,0:14:40.13,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want with her?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.13,0:14:41.81,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from her!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.64,0:14:44.90,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, so mean.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.90,0:14:47.54,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you not to do anything uncalled for?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.54,0:14:49.40,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,And what did you do?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.61,0:14:52.37,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Aw crap! {SSSSSSSSSSSSSHAZBOT}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.65,0:14:54.78,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Sadako!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.61,0:14:59.56,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I think Kazehaya might actually like you after all!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.42,0:15:01.23,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait—!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.23,0:15:03.98,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,What did you—! So loudly too!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.68,0:15:12.14,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,It's a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.14,0:15:14.80,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.35,0:15:19.27,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't "like" in the way you're thinking of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.00,0:15:32.06,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.06,0:15:36.55,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure, but I think Sadako's denying Kazehaya likes her.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.55,0:15:39.22,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.14,0:15:40.96,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Ka—
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.30,0:15:42.63,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.63,0:15:43.38,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.38,0:15:44.97,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are late!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.97,0:15:47.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's already here—
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.42,0:15:49.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why are there so many people here?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.88,0:15:52.09,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Kazeha—
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.36,0:15:52.68,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.68,0:15:53.98,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Come with us!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.98,0:15:55.45,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! This is dangerous!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.45,0:15:56.80,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and just come!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.61,0:15:59.00,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.00,0:16:00.20,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.61,0:16:01.31,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.70,0:16:05.31,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.51,0:16:11.19,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, can we finish the float on time?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.19,0:16:12.98,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,It'll work out.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.98,0:16:15.11,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Seems impossible.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.11,0:16:17.19,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We'll probably have to pull an all-nighter before the festival.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.19,0:16:18.83,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.83,0:16:19.99,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,What, this year too?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.99,0:16:22.75,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What, it was all just talk!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.75,0:16:24.35,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he didn't even say hi to her.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.35,0:16:25.65,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.06,0:16:31.30,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I might not be the right person to say this,{yeah you just shut up, dude}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.09,0:16:35.43,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't think you're saying enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.96,0:16:48.43,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If things keep going like this, will I \Nnever be able to talk to Kazehaya again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.00,0:16:56.96,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will I only be able to watch him walk \Naway without even saying good morning?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.78,0:17:04.71,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He might never smile and say good morning to me again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.96,0:17:08.13,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He might start avoiding me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.19,0:17:14.40,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kazehaya used to be there waiting for me…{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.92,0:17:21.39,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he used to call out to me when I was all alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.40,0:17:36.90,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I might've…
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.90,0:17:38.03,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,done something bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.53,0:17:41.97,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you take that tone with me!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.97,0:17:43.29,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Right…
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.29,0:17:45.35,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Should I sew it shut for you?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.35,0:17:47.92,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,That big mouth of yours?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.92,0:17:49.25,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be troublesome…
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.25,0:17:53.08,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,See, I'm a pretty honest fellow.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.08,0:17:55.35,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.31,0:17:57.53,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Would you move?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.53,0:17:59.02,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the way.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.95,0:18:02.63,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you do this somewhere else?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.97,0:18:07.94,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, Kurumi. What'd you do after that?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.44,0:18:10.44,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,After what?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.92,0:18:14.93,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,After you came to find out what happened between Sadako and Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.93,0:18:15.94,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.26,0:18:20.62,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi, you're not planning something again, are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.62,0:18:22.97,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't do anything to Sawako, did you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.93,0:18:27.28,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I told her off.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.28,0:18:28.50,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,What of it?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.50,0:18:29.83,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.83,0:18:34.00,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with telling off a girl who can't \Neven give a guy chocolates on Valentine's?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.00,0:18:36.61,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Why do you know about that?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.72,0:18:41.59,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Was it your fault?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.59,0:18:44.36,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I interfered!{she dares JAMA-SURU her TAIKANSHIKI}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.36,0:18:46.06,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,But so what?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.55,0:18:49.03,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,She was the one who couldn't give it to him!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.03,0:18:51.35,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't tell her not to give it to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:54.15,Circle Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(456,285)\frz2.27}Kurumi
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.08,0:18:54.30,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,She's got a point. {kurumi has a point}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.30,0:18:56.57,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,No, interfering's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:56.57,Circle Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\frz2.27\pos(853,372)}Kurumi
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:56.57,Circle Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz2.27\pos(215,385)\c&H75C23C&\3c&H9ACC82&}Sawako
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.78,0:18:59.49,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.49,0:19:02.05,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi, you liked Kazehaya too?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.05,0:19:03.60,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Your voice is too loud.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.60,0:19:04.84,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.84,0:19:08.86,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,What? Man, that's tough...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.16,0:19:14.04,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Then if I were to go out with Sadako, wouldn't that be good for you?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.70,0:19:18.34,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get ahead of yourself! {i really love you right now :D:D:D}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.93,0:19:26.77,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you want to get in her way?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.44,0:19:28.77,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I…
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.77,0:19:32.53,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to think that I lost to a girl like her!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.10,0:19:36.90,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think she was so weak!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.90,0:19:38.65,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's disappointing! {i'm disappointed}{IT'S A LET-wait wrong character}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.65,0:19:40.18,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait—!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.18,0:19:41.57,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.61,0:19:52.00,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,So Kazehaya really does like Sadako, doesn't he.{NOOOO SHIIIIIIIIIIIT}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.09,0:19:55.08,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.26,0:19:58.12,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to say that?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.12,0:20:00.33,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave them alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.33,0:20:02.59,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,For Sadako's sake—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.59,0:20:04.40,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,For Sawako?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.91,0:20:06.22,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,More like for yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.09,0:20:12.20,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,So that you can give yourself the satisfaction \Nof saying "I'm such a great guy!"
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.20,0:20:18.36,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how much Sawako suffered just because of you?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.27,0:20:25.77,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You know how badly outsiders can mess things up.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.77,0:20:27.20,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Leave her alone.
